  "body": "There is a \"FlyClient\" proposal that seems to offer an alternative approach for constrained resource clients . The document is at the [this location]( https://eprint.iacr.org/2019/226.pdf) .\r\n\r\nA review would help us understand\r\n\r\n- What it offers\r\n- Should it be implemented and if so how\r\n- What is the effect on the converged light protocols project (bringing Parity and geth in alignment for the future of PIP + LES)",
